quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"Walaqad arsalna ila thamoodaakhahum salihan ani oAAbudoo Allahafa-itha hum fareeqani yakhtasimoon"
  27,46,"Qala ya qawmi limatastaAAjiloona bissayyi-ati qabla alhasanati lawlatastaghfiroona Allaha laAAallakum turhamoon"
  27,47,"Qaloo ittayyarna bikawabiman maAAaka qala ta-irukum AAinda Allahibal antum qawmun tuftanoon"
  27,48,"Wakana fee almadeenati tisAAatu rahtinyufsidoona fee al-ardi wala yuslihoon"
  27,49,"Qaloo taqasamoo billahilanubayyitannahu waahlahu thumma lanaqoolanna liwaliyyihi mashahidna mahlika ahlihi wa-inna lasadiqoon"
  27,50,"Wamakaroo makran wamakarna makranwahum la yashAAuroon"
  27,51,"Fanthur kayfa kanaAAaqibatu makrihim anna dammarnahumwaqawmahum ajmaAAeen"
  27,52,"Fatilka buyootuhum khawiyatan bimathalamoo inna fee thalika laayatanliqawmin yaAAlamoon"
  27,53,"Waanjayna allatheena amanoowakanoo yattaqoon"
  27,54,"Walootan ith qalaliqawmihi ata/toona alfahishata waantum tubsiroon"
  27,55,"A-innakum lata/toona arrijalashahwatan min dooni annisa-i bal antum qawmuntajhaloon"
